{"tid":2472184,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人睇開泰國BL劇(240) 千星大結局","createTime":"2021-04-02T07:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T18:12:42.000Z","uid":231134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7a3e822bfb6a7040ff7bfc7141a5f14072a6ac","tid":2472184,"uid":231134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"<strong>奶巾墮扁Nee！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>歡迎大家有興趣睇泰國BL，一睇BL一去無回頭，溝仔咪？</strong>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">劇透請各位P&rsquo;預先提及劇名並四重加密<br />\n請用不推文回覆<br />\n直播討論期間就唔使加密</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">集各位大成嘅泰BL入坑指南正式推出！</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/lihkgthaiblguide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fview%2Flihkgthaiblguide&d=uw8R2zILh4IVFJjxqgttXLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=0584cb6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/view/lihkgthaiblguide</a><br />\n一次綜合咁多層嘅資料！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/5f/91/3b/5f913bac4294ec43d16ad57304fe4656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F5f%2F91%2F3b%2F5f913bac4294ec43d16ad57304fe4656.jpg&h=7fa05c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">包括：（但唔限於）<br />\nBL必睇推介、2021新劇預告、泰劇FAQ、泰PO字典、巴絲自家製作品、泰文入門教學</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf7BW1o8w6JcMiZBEHKhxZcxWt2sFaf7biEJovzU138B6?filename=TEzXxRw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTEzXxRw.jpg&h=d814b307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰po能夠由2020年發展到依加咁<br />\n實在有賴咁多位P提供嘅資訊同整合<br />\n令更多喺腐海浮沉嘅迷途小羔羊都搵到指路明燈<br />\n繼續一齊搭沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過所謂腐海無涯<br />\n要J嘅泰仔、要update嘅泰腐圈資訊永遠都有<br />\n真係咁多層樓都都裝唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<del><span class=\"x-small\">你又認到以下幾多個仔仔？</span></del><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZyd4drJKjQ9kJWCZXrRW4b4hWVrzRyyL6akwFfCULM2Y?filename=gAasaGE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAasaGE.png&h=90b4089d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然網站目前仲喺起步階段<br />\n但我哋將會繼續更新內容㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmazc3CWUBc83wJABDywkbDHhUzf1G42QFAtG9R5VbiEkF?filename=5eVDhpy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5eVDhpy.jpg&h=5d4c6f27&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><strong><span class=\"green\">靜雞雞話埋你知<br />\n我哋依加整理緊CP字典<br />\n想多啲人知道你嘅本命CP？<br />\n即刻喺下面投稿 之後會放上網站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n</span><a href=\"https://forms.gle/mMBfq4heQZTKAJfc6 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FmMBfq4heQZTKAJfc6%20&d=uw8R2zILh4IVFJjxqgttXLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=91243a5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/mMBfq4heQZTKAJfc6 </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰po出咗名有愛<br />\n只要你肯投稿<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaeTBpKCPqqWJbY75Vrp6EhjNYMMe5mbqahzmA4EVkmu9?filename=YLwrrgY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYLwrrgY.jpg&h=8d9f7a39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論係官配定鬼船<br />\n呢度都無任歡迎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7089f66696f36cdc41d746cf40ef29cbb151ad6","tid":2472184,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"今次會唔會又冇ENG subtitle <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf47ef73e4c2bc724fefb28fa0fe6ce84c1901dd","tid":2472184,"uid":231134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新po無人同我傾偈 我決定要po Gunsmile<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNraegxBvYN1zAAXtHAhKuqTywxUS4qW14yGRamWtA2ib?filename=3DtMHii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DtMHii.jpg&h=77a40bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU4uf6BosakHPtf7qwfds5TVDLDFyhp12qwqXngWv5p6o?filename=RWP0MKZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWP0MKZ.jpg&h=00566515&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfApFHYQWdXmT5SRH9HHobyeCtRyr5DEhE6LwCVTk5QCC?filename=V5Fy6KZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5Fy6KZ.jpg&h=37dc9402&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9ab9ea7c221856941a992478f8aab262f805159","tid":2472184,"uid":296284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf47ef73e4c2bc724fefb28fa0fe6ce84c1901dd","tid":2472184,"uid":231134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新po無人同我傾偈 我決定要po Gunsmile<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3DtMHii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3DtMHii.jpg&h=77a40bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RWP0MKZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWP0MKZ.jpg&h=00566515&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V5Fy6KZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5Fy6KZ.jpg&h=37dc9402&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-02T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Gun哥"},{"pid":"58a62afbba551bea2cf15bfc2d8dbca41e392fd5","tid":2472184,"uid":231134,"like":0,"dislike":0,